data.description: Seller offering $2,000 for updates with favorable offer! Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in the highly sought after Old River Place Subdivision. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this residence is a true gem, with great curb appeal, spacious interior, and modern amenities.. Open concept floor plan with a lovely brick-covered, gas fireplace the living room is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy a newly updated kitchen with a stainless steel fridge, double oven, microwave and dishwasher as well as gorgeous granite countertops. As you walk into the primary bedroom, the vaulted ceilings add a touch of luxury - double vanities in the en suite bathroom accompanied by an expansive walk-in closet. New carpet and paint throughout the rest of the house make it move in ready! The 4th bedroom is on the 2nd floor and perfect for an office or additional bedroom. The backyard is fully fenced in and one of the larger lots in the neighborhood. Schedule your private showing for this beauty today!
